**H2: Does Renters Insurance Cover Your Roommate?**

*Writing instruction:* Open with a direct 40-60 word answer to the primary query. This is the featured snippet target. State clearly that standard renters insurance covers only the named insured on the policy, not anyone else living in the unit. Define "named insured" in one sentence. This section must be complete enough that a reader who reads only this section gets a usable answer.

