**H2: How Much Does Renters Insurance Cost With a Roommate?**

*Writing instruction:* This section addresses the PAA question "renters insurance with roommates cost." Lead with a specific cost figure. Include the cost comparison between shared versus separate policies. This section must include at least one specific numerical benchmark with a date reference. Do not list insurance companies or recommend specific carriers.

